core.tut.pori.http

Class Definitions

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.tut.pori.http.Definitions

  • public final class Definitions
extends java.lang.Object
    Definitions for the http package. In addition to the internally used element definitions, this utility class also contains the common HTTP method names and encodings.
